Subject: backlight: qcom-wled: Add support for WLED5 peripheral that is
Git-commit: 62a1d3f623ac0338912fdfbdda9bdac4cadcbc75
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322
 present on PM8150L PMICs

PM8150L WLED supports the following:
    - Two modulators and each sink can use any of the modulator
    - Multiple CABC selection options from which one can be selected/enabled
    - Multiple brightness width selection (12 bits to 15 bits)

